edu.byu.broderick.fmserver.main.server

Class Handlers

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.byu.broderick.fmserver.main.server.Handlers

  • public class Handlers
extends java.lang.Object
    Container class for Handler objects. Handlers convert from JSON to a server request object and from a response object back to JSON. They also perform some minimal parameter error checking where possible.
    Author:
    Broderick Gardner
